data.description:
Welcome to 5431 Peach Dr, a spacious 5-bedroom home located in the sought-after Woodlands neighborhood in Pace, FL. This stunning property boasts 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for a large family or group of friends. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring all stainless appliances, a quiet dishwasher, smooth top range, built-in microwave, and plenty of counter space for meal prep and entertaining. The interior is beautifully appointed with vinyl flooring throughout and plush carpeting in the bedrooms for added comfort. With 2556 sq ft of living space, there is plenty of room for everyone to spread out and relax. The open floor plan is perfect for hosting gatherings, and the large backyard offers the ideal spot for outdoor activities and relaxation. Conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping, and dining, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this incredible property your new home sweet home!

Minimum Standard Rental Requirements: Showings may be scheduled upon receiving an approved application which entails a credit score of 625 or higher, 3x the monthly rent in qualified income, and 2 years of rental history. First month's rent, a $2,250 security deposit, and a $150 lease processing fee will be due prior to move-in. Up to two pets max, but must be registered and approved with the property manager. The pet rent is $35 a month per pet. The Resident Benefits Package is an additional $50 per month

Smoking allowed:No
